<db:section xml:id="application-permissions">
<db:title>Application Permissions</db:title>
<db:para>The module exposes the Qt C++ <db:link xlink:href="permissions.xml">Application Permissions</db:link> functionality to QML via a set of permission types that can be used to check or request permission in a cross platform manner. See <db:link xlink:href="qml-application-permissions.xml">QML Application Permissions</db:link> for more details.</db:para>
</db:section>
